casebody.data:
Elena STRUJAN, petitioner,
v.
MERCK AND COMPANY, INCORPORATED. No. 13-6591. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 18, 2013. Case below, 532 Fed.Appx. ----. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
